'''萨德勒庭院'''（Sadler's Yard）是英国[[曼彻斯特|曼彻斯特]]的一个公共广场和活动场地。这是[[曼彻斯特市中心|曼彻斯特市中心]]自1996年[[交易广场_(曼彻斯特)|交易广场]]以来第一个新的公共空间，开辟于2015年12月4日<ref>{{cite news |title= Sadler’s Yard Unveiled Ahead Of Pilcrow Pub Launch |url= http://www.manchesterconfidential.co.uk/news/sadlers-yard-unveiled-ahead-of-pilcrow-project-launch |work= Manchester Confidential |date= 3 December 2015 |accessdate= 2016-01-05 |archive-date= 2016-09-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160924212734/http://www.manchesterconfidential.co.uk/news/sadlers-yard-unveiled-ahead-of-pilcrow-project-launch |dead-url= no }}</ref>。位于[[曼彻斯特维多利亚站|曼彻斯特维多利亚站]]对面.<ref>{{cite news |title= Sadler's Yard it is... but the who the 'eck is James Sadler? |url= http://www.manchesterconfidential.co.uk/news/revealed-new-noma-square-named |work= Manchester Confidential |date= 8 September 2015 |accessdate= 2015-12-04 |archive-date= 2016-09-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160925142936/http://www.manchesterconfidential.co.uk/news/revealed-new-noma-square-named |dead-url= no }}</ref> 

该广场以气球主义者，化学家和糕点师詹姆斯·萨德勒命名，他于1785年从曼彻斯特做了第一次载人气球飞行。它是英国第一个通过在线投票命名的公共空间之一<ref>{{cite web |title= Lift off for NOMA square naming |url= http://www.co-operative.coop/corporate/press/press-releases/Estates/lift-off-for-noma-square-naming/ |work= The Co-operative Group |date= 8 September 2015 |accessdate= 2015-12-04 |archive-date= 2016-11-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161119185553/http://www.co-operative.coop/corporate/press/press-releases/Estates/lift-off-for-noma-square-naming/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

